Enum Class PhysicsEventsEnum

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<PhysicsEventsEnum>
cz.cvut.copakond.sweetfluffysheep.model.utils.enums.PhysicsEventsEnum
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<PhysicsEventsEnum>, Constable
public enum PhysicsEventsEnum extends Enum<PhysicsEventsEnum>
Enum representing all possible physics events in the game. This enum is used to handle various events that can occur during the game, such as collisions, rotations, and other interactions.
